    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Level or nearly level areas that occupy the lowers parts of topographical basins. Dry lakes become temporary lakes during periods of rainfall.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
